Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.91,0:00:06.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面——！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.73,0:00:14.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我说
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.04,0:00:16.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二局
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.74,0:00:19.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.84,0:00:22.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微等下啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.97,0:00:26.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面——！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.40,0:00:33.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面有效
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.71,0:00:34.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干得好  武礼叶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.08,0:00:36.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了不起呀  武礼叶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.28,0:00:37.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.53,0:00:42.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小次郎  能不能让我也来比一场
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.30,0:00:45.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  但刚才你说我们再比也没什么意义…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.94,0:00:49.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算啦  我是无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.68,0:00:50.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我去拿护具
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.54,0:00:51.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没在说你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.05,0:00:59.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.86,0:01:03.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  武…武礼…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.27,0:01:04.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.07,0:01:12.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,室江高中一年级  川添珠姬
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.31,0:01:15.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是石桥贤三郎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.86,0:01:19.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,川添珠姬  与我一决胜负吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.05,0:02:58.02,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)}第7话\N寿司与炸肉饼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.32,0:03:02.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一决胜负？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.38,0:03:03.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.82,0:03:04.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.35,0:03:07.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.35,0:03:09.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.10,0:03:13.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么啊  武礼叶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.17,0:03:14.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对吧～你不是吧～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.13,0:03:16.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是先锋川添珠姬吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.15,0:03:17.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.15,0:03:19.42,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.30,0:03:20.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到这种地步你还…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.96,0:03:24.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过是练习赛  再加上我们的交情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.61,0:03:26.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一人身兼二职我也就不说你了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.52,0:03:31.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且不给你准备时间就提出要比赛也是我不对
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.98,0:03:33.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一人身兼二职？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.46,0:03:37.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么啊前辈？我完全听不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.81,0:03:39.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你给我差不多一点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.36,0:03:42.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之  比赛按照这个结果就行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.00,0:03:48.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但要约定要看我与川添珠姬比赛的结果而定
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.56,0:03:51.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈…你那么想要奖杯吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.48,0:03:52.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奖杯…？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.95,0:03:56.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  说起来还有这个呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.83,0:03:58.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么那么想和小珠…？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.71,0:03:59.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.38,0:04:01.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应该懂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.35,0:04:05.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看她  你什么都感觉不到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.66,0:04:17.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经忍不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.91,0:04:21.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果现在不比一场  我是平静不下来的！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.87,0:04:23.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何！要不要和我比一场！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.45,0:04:25.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.18,0:04:27.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.44,0:04:29.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系  小珠  你自己决定吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.23,0:04:33.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈他很强  是很好的练习机会哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.67,0:04:36.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说的不对  小次郎  我不是强
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.65,0:04:38.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今我都没有停止练习过
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.09,0:04:41.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是比以前更强了！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.90,0:04:48.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上啦  小珠
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.41,0:04:50.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊  你也觉得不过瘾吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.94,0:04:54.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家想看小珠比赛啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.14,0:04:57.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打啦  和大人打打看嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.24,0:05:00.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  那我接受
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.63,0:05:10.87,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}川添珠姬 对 石桥贤三郎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.39,0:05:12.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老…老师
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.21,0:05:14.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会变成这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.05,0:05:16.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真有趣！干掉她！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.21,0:05:19.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师！好好关照我的敌人！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.42,0:05:24.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请用茶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.92,0:05:26.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  劳您费心了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.68,0:05:32.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们都很辛苦呢  被老师耍得团团转
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.60,0:05:35.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会不会  这也会成为学习经验
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.92,0:05:38.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就由我和勇次来做裁判
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.82,0:05:39.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.01,0:05:42.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  小次郎  我硬要这样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.54,0:05:48.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽管放手一战吧  珠姬
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.79,0:05:49.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.76,0:05:51.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油啊 小珠～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.72,0:05:53.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师  可不能莽撞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.48,0:06:01.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.23,0:06:16.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人好可怕…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.85,0:06:18.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他想杀了小珠啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.70,0:06:26.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇！竟然打飞了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.61,0:06:29.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师你太过火了！对方又不是男生！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.88,0:06:32.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.27,0:06:35.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不认真打马上就会被得分
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.41,0:06:42.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师…为什么会提出自己上场的要求呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.94,0:06:48.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人…总会有被无法抑制的冲动所支配的时候啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.84,0:06:50.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.03,0:06:51.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.24,0:06:53.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.51,0:06:56.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好成熟！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.62,0:06:57.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个人好成熟！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.46,0:06:59.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠  没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.75,0:07:10.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么…改变了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.86,0:07:15.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.77,0:07:49.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了不起！这种程度也不过才高一吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.26,0:07:54.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了不起！如此了不起的集中力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.59,0:07:58.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当下这家伙的眼睛里根本看不到周围的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.74,0:08:01.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能看到的只有我的动作
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.96,0:08:03.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真羡慕…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.58,0:08:07.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种才能…这股集中力…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.13,0:08:09.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果那时的我有这样的才能…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.26,0:08:17.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面——！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.92,0:08:24.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在我不集中精神搞什么啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.39,0:08:31.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过怎么说也不会输啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.60,0:08:35.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟男女体格有别  体力相差太远
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.27,0:08:37.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更何况手臂长度差太多
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.16,0:08:39.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还不能打赢大人！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.72,0:08:47.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面——！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.43,0:08:52.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面有效
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.61,0:08:54.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好耶！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.17,0:08:56.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.80,0:08:58.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太轻  不算
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.41,0:09:01.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才那样不算吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.74,0:09:05.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是女生再加上单手  给人感觉力道不够
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.71,0:09:08.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且单手本来就不怎么容易拿到分
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.04,0:09:12.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说了  一般女生也不会用啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.53,0:09:15.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师是笨蛋笨蛋笨蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.33,0:09:16.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.29,0:09:18.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准对我的公平裁判有怨言
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.80,0:09:19.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.64,0:09:24.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不服气吗  小珠？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.93,0:09:26.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.38,0:09:31.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这种事情分散注意力…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.06,0:09:33.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你果然还是小孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.76,0:09:36.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露出破绽了  到此为止了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.40,0:09:37.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结束了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.39,0:09:38.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面——…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.10,0:09:47.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手拔击单手击面！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.48,0:09:48.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太帅了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.51,0:09:51.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…好厉害…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.98,0:09:55.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是头一次看到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.19,0:09:58.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是小珠的自尊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.32,0:10:01.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.37,0:10:03.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面有效  没有异议
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.43,0:10:09.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是有点糟糕…？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.41,0:10:12.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说我就要这么输掉了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.98,0:10:14.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞定他！小珠！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.45,0:10:16.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.40,0:10:17.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二局
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.21,0:10:21.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然身材矮小  却已经是出色的剑士
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.79,0:10:34.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此为止了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.27,0:10:37.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈开始认真了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.84,0:10:39.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是小珠恐怕也…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.01,0:10:41.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个架势是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.65,0:10:42.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是上段  小都都
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.48,0:10:44.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师摆出上段…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.36,0:10:46.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是头一次看到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.15,0:10:49.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连和男生练习都没有用过
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.18,0:10:53.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我见识一下吧！小珠！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.95,0:10:55.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠认真起来的力量！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.58,0:10:57.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,见识一下！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.30,0:11:13.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.05,0:11:20.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讲笑话  请到上段道场
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.43,0:11:21.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最高！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.05,0:11:20.06,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（日文谐音冷笑话…）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.58,0:11:27.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.94,0:11:45.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.96,0:11:49.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你发什么呆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.43,0:11:50.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.53,0:11:57.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？我一摆出上段她的集中力一下就断了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.21,0:12:02.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不打了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.84,0:12:03.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.19,0:12:11.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思…突然提出了奇怪的要求
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.89,0:12:14.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你连赛三场也累了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.25,0:12:16.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗？前辈？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.82,0:12:17.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.53,0:12:19.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.36,0:12:23.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小次郎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.93,0:12:26.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚去吃寿司吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.33,0:12:32.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好耶！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.83,0:12:38.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为纪念我们的相识请尝尝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.98,0:12:41.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我家店里做的炸肉饼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.96,0:12:43.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.55,0:12:45.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  正好肚子饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.58,0:12:48.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  横尾你不是才因为吃太多而肚子疼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.35,0:12:50.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一运动就消化啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.43,0:13:03.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃～！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.68,0:13:08.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肉馅味道十足  外皮的硬度也正好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.35,0:13:21.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.85,0:13:23.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  大家也来吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.40,0:13:24.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子都饿了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.93,0:13:26.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要我要
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.48,0:13:27.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不客气了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.46,0:13:30.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不客气了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.24,0:13:31.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好吃！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.95,0:13:35.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  小珠也别客气  请吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.27,0:13:40.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽管拿  你打了那么多场  肚子早饿了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.93,0:13:42.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说…说不出口…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.60,0:13:45.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一个人已经偷偷吃过饭团了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.23,0:13:48.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…那我就不客气了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.21,0:13:52.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为小珠比了三场  所以要吃三个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.18,0:13:54.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三个！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.47,0:13:58.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家做的炸肉饼就算冷掉也很好吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.78,0:14:02.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  也给我一个啊  我说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.15,0:14:05.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活动过身体后的食物真好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.58,0:14:07.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,横尾你不是被秒杀了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.22,0:14:09.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不也输了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.26,0:14:13.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说来  我们取胜的只有浅川一个人而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.98,0:14:16.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说啊  去死好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.62,0:14:17.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.46,0:14:23.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  小次郎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.63,0:14:25.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陪我上松高一趟啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.49,0:14:28.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,松本高中吗  怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.37,0:14:31.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说进来了个很厉害的新人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.01,0:14:33.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.65,0:14:36.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不错啊  这劲头
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.83,0:14:40.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要来一次吗  在这种时代其他学校的人去踢馆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.53,0:14:43.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢！小次郎！理解我的就只有你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.95,0:14:45.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！我们走！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.47,0:14:47.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去踢馆！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.25,0:14:48.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们这些家伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.87,0:14:50.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,踢馆啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.57,0:14:51.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢  走咯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.16,0:14:59.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.33,0:15:02.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们  快点吃啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.42,0:15:06.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次来附近的时候  记得上我们家店里玩哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.00,0:15:08.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你们算便宜哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.58,0:15:10.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.51,0:15:12.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那小次郎  晚上见
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.06,0:15:14.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.05,0:15:16.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果奖杯还是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.04,0:15:19.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  你收着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.90,0:15:34.36,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}抱歉！\N今天还是见不了面了！\N<(  )>
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.44,0:15:37.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种家伙…那种家伙…那种家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.77,0:15:52.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.73,0:15:58.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  小珠
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.68,0:15:59.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说好送你的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.08,0:16:01.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我从老家带来的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.69,0:16:03.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要是动画迷就绝对无法释手的逸品
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.68,0:16:05.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你大概会喜极而泣的吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.44,0:16:06.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不！一定会的！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.26,0:16:15.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,VideoDisk？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.03,0:16:19.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,VHD？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.89,0:16:20.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来说明！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.08,0:16:26.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所谓VHD是1983发行的影像光碟
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.08,0:16:26.11,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(Video High-Density Disc：高密度视频盘)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.45,0:16:29.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由于其低廉的价格与出色的播放能力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.79,0:16:32.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与LD一同受到收藏家们的重视
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.74,0:16:37.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并常作为发售偶像以及动画典藏版的传说中的载体
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.20,0:16:42.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放不进去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.55,0:16:47.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做功课吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.14,0:16:50.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到咯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.29,0:16:53.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寿司寿司  我喜欢～我喜欢～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.84,0:16:54.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.25,0:16:56.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是寿司王
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.19,0:17:07.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  吃啊  小次郎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.84,0:17:10.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  是鲑鱼子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.30,0:17:12.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正宗江户前寿司呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.31,0:17:18.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈老爸开的正宗！江户前！不回转寿司店呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.39,0:17:20.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经没了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.46,0:17:21.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  倒闭了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.58,0:17:25.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是小有名气的店了  怎么可能嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.35,0:17:28.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不过那已经不是老爸的店了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.39,0:17:31.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,转让给别人了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.12,0:17:33.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.60,0:17:40.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人来到店里不过四年就把老爸的手艺学的一分不差
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.26,0:17:47.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了老爸和常客  就连原本要继承店铺的大哥都认同了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.63,0:17:51.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么可以把这间店交付给他
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.28,0:17:55.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爸他安心地退下一线  大哥也自愿退出
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.60,0:18:00.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管在哪里都有天才啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.29,0:18:01.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不管咧！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.39,0:18:02.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我的约定呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.69,0:18:04.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一年免费吃到饱呢？！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.90,0:18:06.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那有什么办法
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.42,0:18:09.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约定上说是老爸的店啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.82,0:18:12.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才说要快点比嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.28,0:18:14.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪你太拖泥带水
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.05,0:18:17.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！把鲑鱼子还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.94,0:18:19.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.33,0:18:21.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是说你知道会这样才说让我吃一年的寿司吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.08,0:18:24.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明知马上就不是你老爸的店了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.84,0:18:25.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.45,0:18:27.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你「唔」了吧？你刚才「唔」了一下吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.14,0:18:29.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好卑鄙！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.37,0:18:32.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来约定都是在骗人！ 根本是幻想！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.96,0:18:36.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么！现在我带你来吃回转寿司你还不感谢我！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.87,0:18:40.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你忘了吗  我还有在另一家学校教剑道啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.77,0:18:41.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.14,0:18:44.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说过的吧  现在兼任两所学校
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.31,0:18:47.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下！你这什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.41,0:18:50.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么也就是说练习赛的对手有两所学校？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.68,0:18:53.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两边不能全部取胜的话约定就不成立吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.59,0:18:58.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  侧身肉、虾和沙丁鱼各来一份
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.97,0:19:02.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  沙丁鱼已经没有了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.82,0:19:05.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  那点什么好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.62,0:19:07.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小次郎  你有什么想吃的可以叫
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.84,0:19:09.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卑鄙！回答我！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.01,0:19:12.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  就是这么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.90,0:19:14.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.83,0:19:17.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为想不怎么可能  所以随口作了约定
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.79,0:19:20.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卑鄙小人！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.79,0:19:22.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你哪里有资格说我！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.68,0:19:23.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.13,0:19:28.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们这样会打扰到其他客人…请安静一点
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.51,0:19:29.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.04,0:19:32.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没资格说我吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.20,0:19:33.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.52,0:19:34.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,川添珠姬啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.14,0:19:36.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.87,0:19:41.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她根本是超实力级别的嘛！你从哪个道场抢来的！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.05,0:19:43.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是抢来的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.36,0:19:45.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是掉下来的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.99,0:19:46.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从天上…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.15,0:19:48.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  你说她？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.30,0:19:51.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  是教导主任…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.10,0:19:54.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼才听得懂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.18,0:19:58.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之让那样的人战两场根本是犯规啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.67,0:20:00.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.79,0:20:03.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就当半斤八两  我就屈尊忍耐一下了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.33,0:20:08.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  请给我黑鲔肚、长鳍鲭、牡丹虾跟…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.74,0:20:11.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！这些全都是525元一盘的东西啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.80,0:20:13.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你给我节制一点！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.79,0:20:17.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有今天了啊！我只有今天能吃了啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.29,0:20:19.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客人…！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.15,0:20:24.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小都你在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.27,0:20:28.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脚底磨破皮了  走路都疼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.52,0:20:31.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  你加入剑道部了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.71,0:20:32.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真稀奇
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.88,0:20:33.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烦死了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.31,0:20:36.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么关系  很合适你嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.80,0:20:37.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不管呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.78,0:20:40.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小都～
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.71,0:20:43.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  我肚子饿了  做饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.30,0:20:48.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？你耳背啊？我说走路都疼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.70,0:20:53.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就没办法了  姐姐我好久也没下厨了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.84,0:20:54.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.87,0:20:57.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通心粉？意大利蔬菜汤？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.38,0:21:01.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好有鸡蛋  那就做蛋炒饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.86,0:21:04.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  我来做
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.25,0:21:06.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想再受到打击了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.54,0:21:07.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.79,0:21:14.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐  吃饭了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.66,0:21:18.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐你坐我DS上啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.82,0:21:22.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起来啦！起来啦姐姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.16,0:21:25.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  笨蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.01,0:21:27.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和彦你干什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.67,0:21:29.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饭好了  走啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.06,0:21:35.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.31,0:21:40.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然熬夜做大家的练习进度表
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.66,0:21:42.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还真是有部长样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.66,0:21:44.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且大家的都还各自独立
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.50,0:21:46.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,部长 is Great！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.02,0:21:50.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  忘了外山和岩佐的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.27,0:21:53.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.75,0:22:03.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡着了…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.52,0:22:09.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电视…忘了关
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.14,0:22:22.82,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fs24\fad(300,0)}I'm Calling the STAR RISE
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.05,0:22:27.84,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}夕闇に  輝き出す  願いたち
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.14,0:22:34.23,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}この手の中 降りてきて 流れ星…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.26,0:22:55.29,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}窓辺で素足のまま  夜を見上げて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.74,0:23:02.32,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}眠れない 月明かり ひとり
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.19,0:23:10.19,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}目の前を ちらついてく 昼間の私
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.80,0:23:17.53,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}自分だけ 空回りで もどかしいまま
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.81,0:23:20.49,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fs24}I'm Calling the STAR RISE
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.78,0:23:25.53,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}目を閉じて  心の声  聞いてる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.82,0:23:32.37,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}まだ知らない 私に出会いたい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.53,0:23:35.37,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fs24}I'm Calling the STAR RISE
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.62,0:23:40.37,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}まばゆく  輝いてる  願いたち
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.70,0:23:48.05,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}この手の中 降りてきて 流れ星…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.14,0:22:22.82,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(300,0)}I'm Calling the STAR RISE
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.05,0:22:27.84,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}暮色中闪耀着的那小小心愿
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.14,0:22:34.23,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}寄于手中  希望流星能为我实现…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.26,0:22:55.29,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}在窗边光着脚丫  仰望着夜空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.74,0:23:02.32,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}唯有无法入眠的月光相伴
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.19,0:23:10.19,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}眼前浮现出午时的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.80,0:23:17.53,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}只是徒劳得令人着急
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.81,0:23:20.49,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm Calling the STAR RISE
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.78,0:23:25.53,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}闭上眼睛倾听心中的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.82,0:23:32.37,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}依然无法得知  它想与我相见
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.53,0:23:35.37,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm Calling the STAR RISE
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.62,0:23:40.37,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}光辉而耀眼的那小小心愿
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.70,0:23:48.05,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}寄于手中  希望流星能为我实现…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.98,0:23:51.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好  我是勇次
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.24,0:23:56.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  上次小次郎老师因为时间缘故  词语接龙没有说完的部分
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.84,0:23:58.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次由我来说
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.36,0:24:00.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  真是没用的大人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.93,0:24:03.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「バ」  啪的一声击中面部
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.77,0:24:06.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「ン」  即使被抱怨肤浅
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.65,0:24:09.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「ブ」  让人私下抱怨不停
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.56,0:24:11.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「レ」  也只求一心练习
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.34,0:24:13.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔  也算完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.68,0:24:16.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集是「小珠和打工」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.03,0:24:19.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,预告中终于看到了那个人的登场！
